Class CubicleController

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.iit.sat.itmd4515.dhalmy.web.CubicleController

    @Named
@SessionScoped
public class CubicleController
extends Object
implements Serializable
    JSF controller for managing cubicles in the application. This controller handles actions related to cubicles, such as displaying, updating, and saving cubicle information.
